      "markdown": "# Example 1\n\n(a) If $f(\\mathbf{\\mathscr{X}})=\\mathbf{\\mathscr{X}}\\mathbf{\\mathscr{e}}^{\\mathbf{\\mathscr{X}}},$ find $f^{\\prime}(x)$ \n\n(b)Find the nth derivative,$f^{(n)}({\\pmb x})$ \n\nSolution:\n\n(a) By the Product Rule, we have \n\n$$f^{\\prime}(x)=\\frac{d}{dx}\\left(x e^{x}\\right)$$\n\n$$=x{\\frac{d}{d x}}\\left(e^{x}\\right)+e^{x}{\\frac{d}{d x}}\\left(x\\right)$$\n\n$$xe^{x}+e^{x}\\cdot1=(x+1)e^{x}$$",
